name: TC_05_18_01 | Verify moving a document to a folder
description: To verify the process of moving a document into a folder.
descriptionHtml: To verify the process of moving a document into a folder.

testStage.description: To verify the process of moving a document into a folder.

steps.name: Click the Settings on the Side Menu
Click on the Billing option in the side menu
A toast message with the text "Plan has been successfully changed." is visible and hidden then
Click the "Documents" item on the left SideMenu
A toast message with the text "Folder created!" is visible and hidden then
Upload file
